Package src.applications

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    FlexfluxCompFVA
    Compares the results of two FVA analyses given a metabolic network, an objective function and two different set of constraints.
    FlexfluxDR
    Finds dead reactions in a given metabolic network.
    FlexfluxFBA
    Computes an FBA analysis given a metabolic network, an objective function and constraints.
    FlexfluxFVA
    Computes an FVA analysis given a metabolic network, an objective function and constraints.
    FlexfluxKO
    Computes an KO analysis given a metabolic network, an objective function and constraints.
    FlexfluxPareto
    The goal of this analysis is to determine what objective (or set of objectives) an organism is optimizing.
    FlexfluxReac
    Computes different FBA analysis given a metabolic network, an objective function and constraints, by making a reaction flux change.
    FlexfluxRFBA
    Computes a time dependent analysis given a metabolic network, an objective function and constraints.
    FlexfluxTest
    Tests the solvers
    FlexfluxTwoReacs
    Computes different FBA analysis given a metabolic network, an objective function and constraints, by making two reactions fluxes change.
